Escrow::constructor
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when config is valid and all addresses are non-zero
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it sets the owner
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it stores feeRecipient, defaultTimeout, platformFeeBps
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it stores middlemanRegistry, soulboundNFT, receiptNFT as immutables
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it initializes dealCounter at 0
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when feeRecipient is address(0)
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__ZeroAddress
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when platformFeeBps exceeds MAX_PLATFORM_FEE_BPS (500)
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__FeeTooHigh
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when defaultTimeout is below MIN_TIMEOUT (1 day)
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__InvalidTimeout
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when middlemanRegistry is address(0)
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__ZeroAddress
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when soulboundNFT is address(0)
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__ZeroAddress
в””в”Ђв”Ђ when receiptNFT is address(0)
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__ZeroAddress

Escrow::createDeal
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when all 3 participants are provided (no address(0) slots)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ given msg.sender is one of the provided addresses
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ given paymentToken is whitelisted
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ given middleman is registered in registry
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ given no two roles share the same address
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it increments dealCounter and returns new dealId
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it stores Deal struct with correct fields
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it sets state to Joined (all slots filled)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it sets middlemanCommissionBps from registry
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it sets platformFeeBps from config
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it sets createdAt to block.timestamp
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it stores timeoutDuration in deadline field (overloaded)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it records msg.sender as deal creator
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it emits DealCreated
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ given client == seller
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__SelfDeal
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ given client == middleman
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__SelfDeal
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ given seller == middleman
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__SelfDeal
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ given middleman is NOT registered in registry
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Registry__NotRegistered
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ given paymentToken is NOT whitelisted
в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__TokenNotAllowed
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ given msg.sender is NOT one of the provided addresses
в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__NotParticipant
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when some participant slots are address(0)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ given msg.sender is one of the non-zero addresses
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it creates deal in Created state (not all slots filled)
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it stores address(0) for empty slots
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it emits DealCreated with address(0) for empty slots
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ given all three addresses are address(0)
в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__NotParticipant
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when amount is 0 (price not yet agreed)
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it creates the deal with amount = 0
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when timeoutDuration is 0
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it uses config.defaultTimeout
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when timeoutDuration is nonzero and >= MIN_TIMEOUT
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it stores the custom timeout duration
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when middleman is address(0)
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it skips middleman registration check
в””в”Ђв”Ђ when paymentToken is address(0)
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__ZeroAddress

Escrow::joinDeal
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal exists
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal is in Created state
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when requested role slot is empty (address(0))
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ given msg.sender does not already hold another role in the deal
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when role is Client
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it sets deal.client to msg.sender
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it emits DealJoined(dealId, msg.sender, Client)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when role is Seller
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it sets deal.seller to msg.sender
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it emits DealJoined(dealId, msg.sender, Seller)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when role is Middleman
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ given msg.sender is registered in registry
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it sets deal.middleman to msg.sender
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it sets middlemanCommissionBps from registry
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it emits DealJoined(dealId, msg.sender, Middleman)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ given msg.sender is NOT registered
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Registry__NotRegistered
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when all slots become filled after joining
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it transitions state from Created to Joined
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ given msg.sender already holds another role
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__SelfDeal
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when requested role slot is already filled
в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__SlotAlreadyFilled
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deal is NOT in Created state
в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__InvalidState
в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deal does not exist
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__DealNotFound

Escrow::cancelDeal
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal exists
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender is the deal creator
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal is in Created state
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it sets state to Resolved with resolution None
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it emits DealCancelled
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal is in Joined state
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it sets state to Resolved with resolution None
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it emits DealCancelled
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal is in Signed state
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__DealNotCancellable
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal is in Funded state
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__DealNotCancellable
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deal is in Resolved state
в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__DealNotCancellable
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender is NOT the deal creator
в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__NotCreator
в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deal does not exist
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__DealNotFound

Escrow::signDeal
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal exists
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal is in Joined state
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender is a participant
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal.amount > 0
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender has NOT already signed
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it records the signature
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it emits DealSigned(dealId, msg.sender)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when this is the 1st or 2nd signature
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it does NOT change deal state
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when this is the 3rd signature (all signed)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚       в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it transitions state to Signed
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚       в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it sets deadline = block.timestamp + stored duration
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it emits DealFullySigned(dealId, deadline)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender has already signed
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__AlreadySigned
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deal.amount == 0
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__InvalidAmount
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender is NOT a participant
в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__NotParticipant
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deal is NOT in Joined state
в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__InvalidState
в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deal does not exist
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__DealNotFound

Escrow::fundDeal
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal exists
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal is in Signed state
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender is the client
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deadline has NOT passed
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when client has sufficient token balance and approval
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it transfers deal.amount from client to escrow via SafeERC20
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it transitions state to Funded
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it emits DealFunded(dealId, client, amount)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when client has insufficient balance or approval
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts (SafeERC20 / ERC20 revert)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deadline HAS passed
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__TimeoutReached
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender is NOT the client
в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__NotClient
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deal is NOT in Signed state
в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__InvalidState
в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deal does not exist
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__DealNotFound

Escrow::confirmDelivery
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal exists
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal is in Funded state
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender is the client
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deadline has NOT passed
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it transitions to DeliveryConfirmed then Resolved
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it sets resolution to Delivery
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it calculates platformFee = floor(amount * platformFeeBps / 10000)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it calculates middlemanFee = floor(amount * commissionBps / 10000)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it credits seller: amount - platformFee - middlemanFee
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it credits middleman: middlemanFee
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it credits feeRecipient: platformFee
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it emits DeliveryConfirmed(dealId, client)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it emits DealResolved(dealId, Delivery, 0, sellerPayout)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it mints SoulboundNFT to middleman
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it mints ReceiptNFT to client
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it mints ReceiptNFT to seller
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deadline HAS passed
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__TimeoutReached
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender is NOT the client
в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__NotClient
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deal is NOT in Funded state
в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__InvalidState
в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deal does not exist
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__DealNotFound

Escrow::requestRefund
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal exists
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal is in Funded state
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender is the client
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deadline has NOT passed
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it transitions state to RefundRequested
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it emits RefundRequested(dealId, client)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deadline HAS passed
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__TimeoutReached
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender is NOT the client
в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__NotClient
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deal is NOT in Funded state
в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__InvalidState
в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deal does not exist
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__DealNotFound

Escrow::acceptRefund
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal exists
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal is in RefundRequested state
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender is the seller
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it transitions state to Resolved
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it sets resolution to Refund
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it credits client pendingBalance with full amount
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it emits RefundAccepted(dealId)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it emits DealResolved(dealId, Refund, amount, 0)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it mints SoulboundNFT to middleman
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it mints ReceiptNFT to client
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it mints ReceiptNFT to seller
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender is NOT the seller
в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__NotSeller
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deal is NOT in RefundRequested state
в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__InvalidState
в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deal does not exist
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__DealNotFound

Escrow::rejectRefund
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal exists
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal is in RefundRequested state
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender is the seller
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it transitions state to Disputed
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it emits DealDisputed(dealId)
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender is NOT the seller
в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__NotSeller
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deal is NOT in RefundRequested state
в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__InvalidState
в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deal does not exist
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__DealNotFound

Escrow::resolveDispute
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal exists
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal is in Disputed state
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender is the middleman
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when resolution is MiddlemanBuyer
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it transitions to Resolved
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it sets resolution to MiddlemanBuyer
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it credits client with full amount (no fees)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it emits DealResolved(dealId, MiddlemanBuyer, amount, 0)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it mints SoulboundNFT to middleman
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it mints ReceiptNFT to client
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it mints ReceiptNFT to seller
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when resolution is MiddlemanSeller
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it transitions to Resolved
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it sets resolution to MiddlemanSeller
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it credits seller: amount - platformFee - middlemanFee
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it credits middleman: middlemanFee
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it credits feeRecipient: platformFee
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it emits DealResolved(dealId, MiddlemanSeller, 0, sellerPayout)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it mints SoulboundNFT to middleman
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it mints ReceiptNFT to client
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it mints ReceiptNFT to seller
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when resolution is None
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__InvalidResolution
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when resolution is Delivery
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__InvalidResolution
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when resolution is Refund
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__InvalidResolution
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when resolution is Timeout
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__InvalidResolution
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender is NOT the middleman
в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__NotMiddleman
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deal is NOT in Disputed state
в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__InvalidState
в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deal does not exist
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__DealNotFound

Escrow::executeTimeout
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal exists
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal is in Funded state
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when block.timestamp > deal.deadline
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it transitions to TimedOut
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it sets resolution to Timeout
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it credits client with full amount (no fees)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it emits DealTimedOut(dealId, msg.sender)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it emits DealResolved(dealId, Timeout, amount, 0)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it mints SoulboundNFT to middleman
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it mints ReceiptNFT to client
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it mints ReceiptNFT to seller
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when block.timestamp <= deal.deadline
в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__TimeoutNotReached
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal is in RefundRequested state
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when block.timestamp > deal.deadline
в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it transitions to TimedOut (same behavior)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal is in Disputed state
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when block.timestamp > deal.deadline
в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it transitions to TimedOut (same behavior)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal is in Created state
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__InvalidState
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal is in Joined state
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__InvalidState
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal is in Signed state
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__InvalidState
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal is in Resolved state
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__InvalidState
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it is callable by anyone (no role restriction)
в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deal does not exist
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__DealNotFound

Escrow::increaseAmount
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal exists
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deal is in Funded state
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender is client or seller
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when newAmount > deal.amount
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when deadline has NOT passed
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when no prior proposal exists
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it records IncreaseProposal(msg.sender, newAmount)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when prior proposal exists from the SAME party
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it overwrites with new IncreaseProposal(msg.sender, newAmount)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when prior proposal exists from OTHER party with SAME newAmount
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it updates deal.amount to newAmount
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it transfers (newAmount - oldAmount) from client to escrow
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it deletes the IncreaseProposal
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it emits AmountIncreased(dealId, oldAmount, newAmount)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when prior proposal exists from OTHER party with DIFFERENT newAmount
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it overwrites with new IncreaseProposal(msg.sender, newAmount)
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deadline HAS passed
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__TimeoutReached
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when newAmount <= deal.amount
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__InvalidAmount
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender is middleman or outsider
в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__NotParticipant
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deal is NOT in Funded state
в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__InvalidState
в””в”Ђв”Ђ when deal does not exist
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__DealNotFound

Escrow::withdraw
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender has nonzero pendingBalance for at least one token
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it transfers each nonzero pending amount to msg.sender via SafeERC20
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it zeros each pendingBalance before transfer (CEI)
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it emits Withdrawal(user, token, amount) for each token
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender has no pendingBalance for any token
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__NothingToWithdraw
в””в”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender has balances from multiple deals
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ it transfers the accumulated total

Escrow::addAllowedToken
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender is owner
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when token is not address(0)
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it adds token to whitelist
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it emits TokenAllowed(token)
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when token is address(0)
в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__ZeroAddress
в””в”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender is NOT owner
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with OwnableUnauthorizedAccount

Escrow::removeAllowedToken
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender is owner
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it removes token from whitelist
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it emits TokenDisallowed(token)
в””в”Ђв”Ђ when msg.sender is NOT owner
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with OwnableUnauthorizedAccount

Escrow::isTokenAllowed
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when token is whitelisted
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it returns true
в””в”Ђв”Ђ when token is not whitelisted
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ it returns false

Escrow::getDeal
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when dealId exists
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it returns the full Deal struct
в””в”Ђв”Ђ when dealId does not exist
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts with Escrow__DealNotFound

Escrow::getDealCount
в””в”Ђв”Ђ it returns the current _dealCounter value

Escrow::pendingBalance
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when user has a pending balance for the token
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it returns the correct amount
в””в”Ђв”Ђ when user has no pending balance
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ it returns 0

Escrow::feeCalculations (fuzz)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ given any valid amount and feeBps
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ platformFee = floor(amount * platformFeeBps / 10000)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ middlemanFee = floor(amount * commissionBps / 10000)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ sellerPayout = amount - platformFee - middlemanFee
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ sellerPayout + platformFee + middlemanFee == amount (invariant)
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ given amount = 0
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ all fees are 0
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ given amount = 1
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ all fees are 0 (floor rounding)
в””в”Ђв”Ђ given amount = type(uint96).max
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ no overflow occurs

Escrow::stateMachineIntegrity
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ valid transitions
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Created в†’ Joined (via joinDeal filling last slot)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Joined в†’ Signed (via signDeal third signature)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Signed в†’ Funded (via fundDeal)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Funded в†’ DeliveryConfirmed (via confirmDelivery)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Funded в†’ RefundRequested (via requestRefund)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Funded в†’ TimedOut (via executeTimeout)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ DeliveryConfirmed в†’ Resolved (via _resolveDeal)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ RefundRequested в†’ Disputed (via rejectRefund)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ RefundRequested в†’ Resolved (via acceptRefund)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ RefundRequested в†’ TimedOut (via executeTimeout)
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Disputed в†’ Resolved (via resolveDispute)
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ Disputed в†’ TimedOut (via executeTimeout)
в””в”Ђв”Ђ invalid transitions
    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ no backward transitions (Joined в†’ Created, Funded в†’ Signed, etc.)
    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ no skip transitions (Created в†’ Signed, Created в†’ Funded, etc.)
    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Resolved в†’ any (terminal, no outgoing transitions)
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ TimedOut в†’ any (terminal, no outgoing transitions)

Escrow::reentrancy
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ fundDeal with reentrant token callback
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts due to ReentrancyGuardTransient
в””в”Ђв”Ђ withdraw with reentrant token callback
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ it reverts due to ReentrancyGuardTransient
